{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/hoaxes/myths-about-erouska-app","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Myths about eRouška app","meta_description":"The eRouška app does not collect and save GPS data.","content":{"processed":"<p><strong>The eRouška app is being used to monitor the population</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Hoax: </strong>Different variations of the statement: <em>“eRouška is being used to watch people.”</em></p>\n<p><strong>Explanation: </strong>The eRouška app does <strong>not collect and save GPS data</strong>, but the <strong>Android operating system does include</strong> some Bluetooth LE (low energy) services that eRouška needs to function within location services- specifically Google Play Services. This is why the user needs to agree to the app having access to certain location data. <strong>This is not necessary for users with the iOS operating system. </strong>Why the location services need to be on is explained by <strong><a href=\"https://support.google.com/android/answer/9930236\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">google here (in Czech). </a></strong></p>\n<p>For the app to work, you <strong>only need to turn on Bluetooth</strong>( for both iOS and Android).</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/hoaxes/myths-about-erouska-app"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-09T15:03:35+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://erouska.cz/","title":"Information about eRouška app "},{"uri":"https://erouska.cz/caste-dotazy","title":"Časté dotazy na tvůrce aplikace."}],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia","drupal_internal__tid":"33"}],"icon":{"code":"warning"},"situation_type":{"name":"Hoaxes","path":{"alias":"/situations/hoaxes"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"record_voice_over"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2020-11-09T16:05:20+01:00"},"situationArea